creator: GIR Logistics Pvt. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
GIR was established by our founder Late Sh. Moti Ram Singal in 1965. From a humble beginning, starting with just one office in Delhi, GIR has now grown into a multi-modal logistics company, having presence across India and globe.

We cherish the ideals set by our Late Chairman Sh. Moti Ram Singal, of high integrity, sincerity, customer first approach & taking care of all stakeholders. Our approach focuses on how we deliver operational excellence to provide viable, cost-effective technology-enabled solutions to the most challenging logistics & supply chain management issues.

TMS APP (Transport Management System Application) is an integrated solution developed for managing all activities performed on day-to-day basis in a Logistics business. It integrates and streamlines logistics business planning, execution, freight payment, and business process automation on a single mobile application. The solution is designed to lowers operational costs, improves customer service and centralized monitoring and control. The solution is an integrated solution which comprise of Client Work Order, Bidding, Purchase Order, HRMS and CRM, etc. AXP APP provides accurate and timely information thus assuring faster decision-making and better.
descriptionShort: TMS App is an integrated solution for day-to-day basis in a Logistics business.
